1
00:00:02,260 --> 00:00:06,580
Welcome to Zelda's Adventure, an action-adventure role-playing game.

2
00:00:07,379 --> 00:00:12,053
As a player, you will adopt the personality of our heroine Princess Zelda.

3
00:00:12,719 --> 00:00:17,673
To play the game succesfully, you must explore the great land of Tolemac.

4
00:00:18,267 --> 00:00:20,993
To control Zelda's movement around Tolemac

5
00:00:21,266 --> 00:00:26,426
move the controller left, right, up, down and diagonally.

6
00:00:27,307 --> 00:00:29,293
The court astronomer Gaspra

7
00:00:29,333 --> 00:00:33,413
will introduce the story of Zelda and describe how her quest came about.

8
00:00:33,751 --> 00:00:36,665
He will also reappear every time

9
00:00:36,746 --> 00:00:40,320
Zelda has succesfully completed an underworld shrine

10
00:00:40,573 --> 00:00:44,361
and collected one of seven treasured Celestial Signs.

11
00:00:45,166 --> 00:00:48,859
Another mentor and guide to Zelda is me Shurmak.

12
00:00:49,107 --> 00:00:52,254
Throughout the game I help orient Zelda and guide her.

13
00:00:53,039 --> 00:00:57,426
While exploring, Zelda will encounter many enemies that inhabit this land.

14
00:00:57,700 --> 00:01:01,474
She must defeat them by using skill and speed.

15
00:01:01,970 --> 00:01:03,977
Zelda attacks them with her wand.

16
00:01:04,396 --> 00:01:08,230
You employ the wand by pressing Action Button 1.

17
00:01:09,057 --> 00:01:13,526
If Zelda is succesful at defeating her enemies, she will be rewarded.

18
00:01:13,776 --> 00:01:16,129
They will randomly drop rubies and hearts

19
00:01:16,154 --> 00:01:19,843
that will increase her currency and life units respectively.

20
00:01:20,639 --> 00:01:23,159
Rubies which are the currency of Tolemac

21
00:01:23,500 --> 00:01:25,288
can be used to buy useful items

22
00:01:25,312 --> 00:01:28,867
and are indicated on the top-left corner of the screen.

23
00:01:29,516 --> 00:01:34,176
Hearts are the life units that give Zelda strength to fight throughout the game.

24
00:01:34,602 --> 00:01:38,068
They are represented on the upper-right corner of the play screen.

25
00:01:38,688 --> 00:01:44,361
To select an object or a weapon on the inventory screen, press Action Button 2.

26
00:01:45,297 --> 00:01:47,365
Once in the inventory screen

27
00:01:47,438 --> 00:01:50,371
you can access useful items and weapons

28
00:01:50,416 --> 00:01:54,936
by selecting an object with your cursor and the pressing Action Button 1.

29
00:01:55,706 --> 00:01:59,660
Treasures and weapons can be scrolled by pressing the left window button

30
00:01:59,685 --> 00:02:03,766
to move left, and by pressing the right window button to move right.

31
00:02:04,601 --> 00:02:09,218
The weapon in use appears in the window in the lower right of the inventory screen.

32
00:02:09,977 --> 00:02:13,584
If you select a useful item from the treasures selection

33
00:02:13,859 --> 00:02:18,067
the item will appear in the same window where the weapon selection appeared.

34
00:02:18,289 --> 00:02:22,688
Zelda can use only one item or weapon at a time.

35
00:02:23,514 --> 00:02:27,267
In Zelda's travels she will find many locked doors.

36
00:02:27,664 --> 00:02:31,750
She must have a key in her possession to pass through these locked entrances.

37
00:02:32,096 --> 00:02:36,029
The number of keys in Zelda's possession will appear in the small window

38
00:02:36,188 --> 00:02:38,968
in the upper right of the inventory screen.

39
00:02:39,411 --> 00:02:41,331
To help navigate through Tolemac

40
00:02:41,610 --> 00:02:45,510
a map is available by moving your joystick to the map button

41
00:02:45,630 --> 00:02:48,337
and then pressing your Action Button 1.

42
00:02:49,269 --> 00:02:50,750
There are two types of maps:

43
00:02:51,089 --> 00:02:54,862
One for the overworld and one for each of the underworlds.

44
00:02:55,210 --> 00:02:59,330
The map for the overworld will reveal where you are and where you have traveled.

45
00:03:00,105 --> 00:03:04,666
The maps for each of the underworlds will reveal where you are

46
00:03:04,727 --> 00:03:08,753
where you have traveled, and where you need to go to complete your quest.

47
00:03:09,522 --> 00:03:13,776
To return to gameplay, press Action Button 2.

48
00:03:14,168 --> 00:03:16,215
When you are ready to exit game

49
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:20,449
move your cursor to exit button and press Action Button 1.

50
00:03:21,489 --> 00:03:25,329
You will then arrive at the save, continue and quit screen.

51
00:03:25,730 --> 00:03:27,770
To activate any of these buttons

52
00:03:27,795 --> 00:03:32,203
you must move the cursor to the button and press Action Button 1.

53
00:03:33,597 --> 00:03:37,964
If you save and quit, you will arrive at the player select screen

54
00:03:38,015 --> 00:03:41,533
where you have to option to play again or exit game.

55
00:03:42,307 --> 00:03:44,050
When you come back to play again

56
00:03:44,237 --> 00:03:47,724
you can restart where you left off by selecting your name.

57
00:03:48,658 --> 00:03:51,885
You will then return to the first screen of gameplay

58
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:55,506
with all items and weapons still in the inventory.

59
00:03:56,393 --> 00:04:01,430
If you quit without save, you will arrive at the player select screen

60
00:04:01,483 --> 00:04:05,096
where you have to option to play again or exit game.

61
00:04:06,025 --> 00:04:07,872
When you return to gameplay

62
00:04:07,897 --> 00:04:10,790
you will not be able to return to your previous game.

63
00:04:10,848 --> 00:04:15,809
However, your status will be fled the last game you saved.

64
00:04:16,586 --> 00:04:18,319
If you choose Return to Game

65
00:04:18,383 --> 00:04:22,463
you will arrive at the inventory screen where you press Action Button 2

66
00:04:22,563 --> 00:04:24,616
which then returns you to gameplay.

67
00:04:25,036 --> 00:04:29,103
Before each game, you must select a name for your hero or heroine.

68
00:04:29,633 --> 00:04:33,506
You can choose the create button by moving the cursor onto the button

69
00:04:33,682 --> 00:04:36,015
and pressing Action Button 1.

70
00:04:36,954 --> 00:04:39,364
This takes you to the enter name screen

71
00:04:39,388 --> 00:04:41,814
where you type in your name on the keyboard

72
00:04:41,869 --> 00:04:45,489
by selecting the desired letters with Action Button 1

73
00:04:45,533 --> 00:04:48,142
and then moving your cursor to the done button

74
00:04:48,196 --> 00:04:50,896
and pressing Action Button 1 again.

75
00:04:52,042 --> 00:04:54,875
This takes you back to the player select screen.

76
00:04:55,266 --> 00:04:58,145
Here you press play by selecting the play button

77
00:04:58,259 --> 00:05:00,446
and pressing Action Button 1.

78
00:05:00,964 --> 00:05:03,064
You will then begin the game.

79
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:07,580
To delete a player's name, place the cursor on the delete button

80
00:05:07,682 --> 00:05:12,295
and press Action Button 1 for a three second duration.

81
00:05:13,397 --> 00:05:17,170
To exit game, place the cursor on the exit button

82
00:05:17,231 --> 00:05:19,038
and press Action Button 1.

83
00:05:19,329 --> 00:05:22,149
That is all I will reveal for now.

84
00:05:22,663 --> 00:05:25,263
The rest is up to you to discover.

